cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DB 

This paper discusses an architecture for probabilistic concept-based information retrieval, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The architecture also makes use of probabilistic networks technology, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the knowledge acquisition component mentioned in the paper is related to database systems (cs.DB).
